description: For sale: $424,900. Mahtomedi schools. If you like to store your toys inside or like to work on them this home is for you, the 3 + Stall garage has heated floors and 10' ceilings and more-check it out now! 5 bedroom, 4 bathroom home with newer addition and total remodel in Mahtomedi school district. All tile floors are heated. Solid hardwood floors, wood panel doors. Impressive stairway. Living room and family room wired for surround sound. The warmth of aspen throughout house. Living, kitchen and dining area have vaulted ceilings. Granite, marble, and tile througout home. Master bedroom and bathroom with a huge 13' x 8' walk-in closet, and a 6' x 6' travertine and porcelain tiled shower with heated floors and multiple shower heads. Oversized mechanics garage for vehicles/toys has a 10' ceiling, 3+ stalls with three 9' x 10' wide doors, compressed air wheels, HEATED floor with DRAINS, steel I-beam and chain hoist to work on toys or lift engines. Bathroom ready for you to finish. Outside you will feel transported to the northwoods with custom rockscaping, 24' x 16' cement deck, and lower 15' x 12' marble patio with fire-pit. See supplement for the upgrades of this wonderful home
